channel.title: Wilderness Guardians [BETA ONLINE]
channel.description:
[center][img]http://img841.imageshack.us/img841/3821/bannerysa.png[/img][/center] [center]Today I'm showing you the new server coming soon called Wilderness Guardians! This is a Project Insanity source off of HyBrId PvP. So here is some info!
[size=36pt]BETA IS [color=red]OFFLINE[/color]! THIS IS DUE TO VPS UPDATING.[/size]
~[u]Staff[/u]~ [img]http://i34.tinypic.com/2j2w903.jpg[/img][u]Owners[/u][img]http://i34.tinypic.com/2j2w903.jpg[/img] XLdarkwingLX RSaleh
[center] ~[u]Basic Information[/u]~ Founder: XLdarkwingLX Co Scripter(s): RSaleh Other Helper(s): Owner Nitro Version: 1.0 Type: 317 Project Insanity Original Source: HyBriD PvP Beta Release: [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/serverstatus.php?server=guardians317.no-ip.org]MoparScape Status Page[/url] Official Release: Unkown[/center]
[center]~[u]Update Log[/u]~
[ul][li]Added better following[/li] [li]Acquired new god armours[/li] [li]Dungeoneering first 3 levels are finished[/li] [li]Dungeoneering player tokens complete[/li] [li]Other minor glitches fixed[/li] [li]Got Hybrid PvP new source[/li] [li]Ancient God Items added in[/li] [li]All Soul Wars pets added![/li] [li]Webclient[/li] [li]Abyssal Minion & Minitrice Dialogue[/li] [li]Started working on actual summoning familiars[/li] [li]Started making new skilling zone[/li] [li]Started making new home[/li] [li]Finished new home and about half way skilling zone[/li] [li]Fixed some glitches and changed the shops[/li] [li]XP Rates changed[/li] [li]Summoning started, familiars work 33.3%[/li] [li]Got the familiar calling down to 1 error, easy fix[/li] [li]12 more summoning familiars to go till summoning beta release.[/li][/ul] [/center]
[center]~[u]What we've accomplished[/u]~ Well, its been about 2 weeks since we first started this project and we haven't gotten far. We have done a lot of the basic stuff such as renaming, moving NPCs, moving homes, editing shops, etc. We have also started on clipped following and that will soon be finished. Another thing we've started on is Dungeoneering. Theres more information below on this.[/center]
[center]~[u]What we're working on[/u]~ We are working on a lot at the moment. Like summoning (working on the rest of the pets) the onto pouches. We have a pic of a new interface made by owner nitro below in the picture section. We are also going for a Dungeoneering thing. Don't know how good its going to be but what ever! Right now I'm working on BoB (beast of burden) cause we're going to add the summoning familiars (the actual pouches). After that I will work on summons attacking other players/npcs in multi combat area. I also want to make an HD client (full screen). So we got a lot to do! Beta released tomorrow if all goes well!
Familiar Beast of Burden: |||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||| ~ Interface gotten ~ 15%
Familiar Attacking (PvN & NvN): |||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||| ~ Unstarted ~ 0%
BoB: |||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||| ~ 15%
Webclient HD: |||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||| ~ Unstarted ~ 0%
Dungeoneering: |||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||| ~ 30%
Clipped Following: |||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||| ~ 50%
Site: |||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||| ~ 50%
[center]~[u]Dungeoneering[/u]~ No, this will not be some crappy Dungeoneering some kid just threw together where all you do is run through monsters and go to the end. Thats not it at all. We are currently designing a great base for it. And yes, we have the actual bosses and monsters (thanks to iHybrid PvP). We are currently working on adding the animations to them (mostly bosses) and making more floors. We also have all 3 caps (Trimmed, Untrimmed, masters (thanks to iHybrid again). I will try to make it so that you can't bring any weapons in but you can get the actual dungeoneering items inside the dungeons (that will probably come out later after we release it). You won't be able to teleport out and I'm planning on making a mining and smithing thing in there to get the items. We also need to make the shops and dialogues but that will be soon.[/center]
[center]~[u]More about us[/u]~ When it comes to sloppy work I don't tolerate it on my server. When I release something I guarantee it will be good and worthy of being used. We want the best for our users so they can actually play instead of just being bored and doing nothing. Yes, this is a 2 man project but we will get it online soon and maybe even release it if it hits off. If you have any suggestions or links to things that you think may help us, please post them or PM me them. Also if you have any comments or questions.[/center]
[center]~[u]Pictures[/u]~ The Site [img]http://img717.imageshack.us/img717/7825/newsiteb.png[/img]
Welcome! [img]http://img854.imageshack.us/img854/1807/welcomep.png[/img]
Stats [img]http://img545.imageshack.us/img545/4290/equipr.png[/img]
SW Pets! [img]http://img20.imageshack.us/img20/7514/minitrice.png[/img]
Skilling [img]http://img535.imageshack.us/img535/1213/mininge.png[/img] [img]http://img820.imageshack.us/img820/8239/fishingf.png[/img] [img]http://img822.imageshack.us/img822/2485/farmin.png[/img] [img]http://img825.imageshack.us/img825/2851/agiltiy.png[/img] [img]http://img638.imageshack.us/img638/2176/18027186.png[/img]
New Summoning Interface (Made by Owner Nitro) [img]http://img94.imageshack.us/img94/3076/smexyinterface.png[/img][/center]
[center]~[u]Help us get started[/u]~ With a donation of $1, we can get up and running to public sooner! Please help us out!
Donate with Mobile Phone [url=https://www.onebip.com/tinyurl/e71e393b011c7695be721831c1834892][img]http://www.onebip.com/tools/bts/btn06.gif[/img][/url]
Donate with Paypal [url=https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_s-xclick&hosted_button_id=6P58AXNZBAMNA][img]https://www.paypalobjects.com/WEBSCR-640-20110401-1/en_US/i/btn/btn_donateCC_LG.gif[/img][/url]
Please donate to help keep the server running. When you donate, you get donor status, as long as you donate $8. Otherwise its worthless...[/center]
[center]Thank you for looking at our devo page! If you need any help or support please, don't hesitate to contact xldarkwinglx@yahoo.com! Thanks for you participation![/center]
